function Rn(e) {
    return e.split("-")[0]

    return e.split("-")[1]

function Xd(e) {
    return e === "x" ? "y" : "x"

function Jd(e) {
    return e === "y" ? "height" : "width"

function Dc(e) {
    return e.replace(/start|end/g, t => $E[t])

const eh = ["left", "right"]
  , th = ["right", "left"]
  , VE = ["top", "bottom"]
  , UE = ["bottom", "top"];
function HE(e, t, n) {
    switch (e) {
    case "top":

    case "right":

    default:

    }

function GE(e, t, n, r) {

function Wa(e) {

function Ba(e) {
    const {x: t, y: n, width: r, height: o} = e;

function nh(e, t, n) {
    let {reference: r, floating: o} = e;
    const i = nn(t)
      , s = Zd(t)
      , a = Jd(s)
      , l = Rn(t)
      , u = i === "y"
      , f = r.x + r.width / 2 - o.width / 2
      , p = r.y + r.height / 2 - o.height / 2
      , y = r[a] / 2 - o[a] / 2;
    let g;
    switch (l) {
    case "top":
        g = {
            x: f,
            y: r.y - o.height
        };
        break;
    case "bottom":
        g = {
            x: f,
            y: r.y + r.height
        };
        break;
    case "right":
        g = {
            x: r.x + r.width,
            y: p
        };
        break;
    case "left":
        g = {
            x: r.x - o.width,
            y: p
        };
        break;
    default:
        g = {
            x: r.x,
            y: r.y
        }
    }
    switch (oi(t)) {
    case "start":
        g[s] -= y * (n && u ? -1 : 1);
        break;
    case "end":
        g[s] += y * (n && u ? -1 : 1);
        break
    }
    return g
}

function dT(e, t) {
    const n = Math.abs(t.top - e.y)
      , r = Math.abs(t.bottom - e.y)
      , o = Math.abs(t.right - e.x)
      , i = Math.abs(t.left - e.x);
    switch (Math.min(n, r, o, i)) {
    case i:
        return "left";
    case o:
        return "right";
    case n:
        return "top";
    case r:
        return "bottom";
    default:
        throw new Error("unreachable")
    }
}
function fT(e, t, n=5) {
    const r = [];
    switch (t) {
    case "top":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y + n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break;
    case "bottom":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y - n
        });
        break;
    case "left":
        r.push({
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break;
    case "right":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break
    }
    return r
}

function hT(e, t) {

}

function gT(e) {
    if (e.length <= 1)
        return e.slice();

    for (let r = 0; r < e.length; r++) {
        const o = e[r];
        for (; t.length >= 2; ) {
            const i = t[t.length - 1]
              , s = t[t.length - 2];
            if ((i.x - s.x) * (o.y - s.y) >= (i.y - s.y) * (o.x - s.x))
                t.pop();
            else
                break
        }
        t.push(o)
    }
    t.pop();
    const n = [];
    for (let r = e.length - 1; r >= 0; r--) {
        const o = e[r];
        for (; n.length >= 2; ) {
            const i = n[n.length - 1]
              , s = n[n.length - 2];

                n.pop();
            else
                break
        }
        n.push(o)
    }

    t.length === 1 && n.length === 1 && t[0].x === n[0].x && t[0].y === n[0].y ? t : t.concat(n)
}

var Rl = class {
    constructor() {
        this.listeners = new Set,
        this.subscribe = this.subscribe.bind(this)
    }
    subscribe(e) {
        return this.listeners.add(e),
        this.onSubscribe(),
        () => {
            this.listeners.delete(e),
            this.onUnsubscribe()
        }
    }
    hasListeners() {
        return this.listeners.size > 0
    }
    onSubscribe() {}
    onUnsubscribe() {}
}

function Sh(e, t) {
    const {type: n="all", exact: r, fetchStatus: o, predicate: i, queryKey: s, stale: a} = e;
    if (s) {
        if (r) {
            if (t.queryHash !== mf(s, t.options))
                return !1
        } else if (!as(t.queryKey, s))
            return !1
    }

        const l = t.isActive();
        if (n === "active" && !l || n === "inactive" && l)
            return !1
    }
    return !(typeof a == "boolean" && t.isStale() !== a || o && o !== t.state.fetchStatus || i && !i(t))
}
function Ch(e, t) {
    const {exact: n, status: r, predicate: o, mutationKey: i} = e;
    if (i) {
        if (!t.options.mutationKey)
            return !1;

                return !1
        } else if (!as(t.options.mutationKey, i))

    }

}
function mf(e, t) {

function ss(e) {

function as(e, t) {
    return e === t ? !0 : typeof e != typeof t ? !1 : e && t && typeof e == "object" && typeof t == "object" ? Object.keys(t).every(n => as(e[n], t[n])) : !1
}
function Iw(e, t) {
    if (e === t)
        return e;
    const n = Eh(e) && Eh(t);
    if (n || $c(e) && $c(t)) {

          , o = r.length

          , s = i.length

            u++) : (a[p] = Iw(e[p], t[p]),

        }

    }

}
function Eh(e) {
    return Array.isArray(e) && e.length === Object.keys(e).length
}
function $c(e) {
    if (!kh(e))
        return !1;
    const t = e.constructor;
    if (t === void 0)

}
function kh(e) {

zn = function(t) {
    const n = r => {
        switch (t.type) {
        case "failed":
            return {
                ...r,
                failureCount: t.failureCount,
                failureReason: t.error
            };
        case "pause":
            return {
                ...r,
                isPaused: !0
            };
        case "continue":
            return {
                ...r,
                isPaused: !1
            };
        case "pending":
            return {
                ...r,
                context: t.context,
                data: void 0,
                failureCount: 0,
                failureReason: null,
                error: null,
                isPaused: t.isPaused,
                status: "pending",
                variables: t.variables,
                submittedAt: Date.now()
            };
        case "success":
            return {
                ...r,
                data: t.data,
                failureCount: 0,
                failureReason: null,
                error: null,
                status: "success",
                isPaused: !1
            };
        case "error":
            return {
                ...r,
                data: void 0,
                error: t.error,
                failureCount: r.failureCount + 1,
                failureReason: t.error,
                isPaused: !1,
                status: "error"
            }
        }
    }
    ;
    this.state = n(this.state),
    Qe.batch( () => {
        j(this, qt).forEach(r => {
            r.onMutationUpdate(t)
        }
        ),
        j(this, Ye).notify({
            mutation: this,
            type: "updated",
            action: t
        })
    }
    )
}

function eo(e) {

function zh(e, t="") {

function bi(e, t) {

        return e.one;

}

  , Ef = ["воскресенье", "понедельник", "вторник", "среду", "четверг", "пятницу", "субботу"];
function Dj(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    switch (e) {
    case 0:
        return "'в прошлое " + t + " в' p";
    case 1:
    case 2:
    case 4:
        return "'в прошлый " + t + " в' p";
    case 3:
    case 5:
    case 6:
        return "'в прошлую " + t + " в' p"
    }
}
function Hh(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    return e === 2 ? "'во " + t + " в' p" : "'в " + t + " в' p"
}
function _j(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    switch (e) {
    case 0:
        return "'в следующее " + t + " в' p";
    case 1:
    case 2:
    case 4:
        return "'в следующий " + t + " в' p";
    case 3:
    case 5:
    case 6:
        return "'в следующую " + t + " в' p"
    }
}
const Aj = {
    lastWeek: (e, t, n) => {
        const r = e.getDay();
        return Uh(e, t, n) ? Hh(r) : Dj(r)
    }
    ,
    yesterday: "'вчера в' p",
    today: "'сегодня в' p",
    tomorrow: "'завтра в' p",
    nextWeek: (e, t, n) => {
        const r = e.getDay();
        return Uh(e, t, n) ? Hh(r) : _j(r)
    }
    ,
    other: "P"
}
  , Ij = (e, t, n, r) => {
    const o = Aj[e];
    return typeof o == "function" ? o(t, n, r) : o
}

  , iO = ["Пн", "Вт", "Ср", "Чт", "Пт", "Сб", "Вс"];
function sO({tasks: e, onTaskCreate: t, onTaskUpdate: n, onTaskArchive: r, getTasksForDate: o, openDaySidebar: i}) {
    const [s,a] = d.useState(new Date)
      , [l,u] = d.useState(null)
      , [f,p] = d.useState(!1)
      , [y,g] = d.useState(null)
      , [b,m] = d.useState("")
      , x = d.useMemo( () => e.filter(T => !T.isArchived && (T.title.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase()) || T.description && T.description.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase()) || T.tags && T.tags.some(F => F.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase())))), [e, b])
      , w = mr(s, {
        weekStartsOn: 1
    })
      , h = R2(s, {
        weekStartsOn: 1
    })
      , v = [];
    let S = w;
    for (; S <= h; )
        v.push(S),
        S = Ih(S, {
            days: 1
        });
    const C = T => {
        a(F => Ih(F, {
            weeks: T === "prev" ? -1 : 1
        }))
    }
      , k = T => {
        i(T)
    }
      , E = (T, F) => {
        F.stopPropagation(),
        g(T),
        u(null),
        p(!0)
    }
      , N = T => {
        y ? n(y.id, T) : l && t({
            ...T,
            dueDate: l
        }),
        p(!1)
    }
      , O = T => {
        switch (T) {
        case "high":
            return "bg-priority-high";
        case "medium":
            return "bg-priority-medium";
        case "low":
            return "bg-priority-low";
        default:
            return "bg-muted"
        }
    }
    ;
    return c.jsxs("div", {
        className: "h-full flex flex-col",
        children: [c.jsxs("div", {
            className: "flex items-center justify-between p-4 border-b",
            children: [c.jsxs("div", {
                className: "flex items-center gap-4",
                children: [c.jsx(Ue, {
                    variant: "outline",
                    size: "icon",
                    onClick: () => C("prev"),
                    children: c.jsx(ey, {
                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                    })
                }), c.jsxs("h2", {
                    className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                    children: [Vh(w, "d MMMM", {
                        locale: Gh
                    }), " - ", Vh(h, "d MMMM yyyy", {
                        locale: Gh
                    })]
                }), c.jsx(Ue, {
                    variant: "outline",
                    size: "icon",
                    onClick: () => C("next"),
                    children: c.jsx(ty, {
                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                    })
                })]
            }), c.jsx("div", {
                className: "w-1/3",
                children: c.jsx($t, {
                    placeholder: "Поиск...",
                    value: b,
                    onChange: T => m(T.target.value)
                })
            })]
        }), c.jsx("div", {
            className: "flex-1 p-4",
            children: c.jsxs("div", {
                className: "grid grid-cols-7 gap-1",
                children: [iO.map(T => c.jsx("div", {
                    className: "p-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground",
                    children: T
                }, T)), v.map( (T, F) => {
                    const I = new Date().toDateString() === T.toDateString()
                      , U = o(T).filter(M => x.includes(M));
                    return c.jsx(ot, {
                        className: L("min-h-[100px] p-2 cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50", I && "ring-2 ring-primary"),
                        onClick: () => k(T),
                        children: c.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "flex flex-col h-full",
                            children: [c.jsx("span", {
                                className: L("text-sm font-medium mb-1", I && "text-primary font-bold"),
                                children: T.getDate()
                            }), c.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex-1 space-y-1",
                                children: [U.slice(0, 3).map(M => c.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: L("p-1 rounded text-xs cursor-pointer hover:opacity-80 text-white", O(M.priority), M.completed && "opacity-50 line-through"),
                                    onClick: G => E(M, G),
                                    children: [M.title.substring(0, 20), M.title.length > 20 && "..."]
                                }, M.id)), U.length > 3 && c.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "text-xs text-muted-foreground",
                                    children: ["+", U.length - 3, " еще"]
                                })]
                            }), U.length === 0 && c.jsx("div", {
                                className: "flex-1 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity",
                                children: c.jsx(ml, {
                                    className: "h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground"
                                })
                            })]
                        })
                    }, F)
                }
                )]
            })
        }), c.jsx(Fl, {
            open: f,
            onOpenChange: p,
            task: y,
            selectedDate: l,
            onSubmit: N,
            onArchive: r
        })]
    })
}
const li = () => {
    const [e,t] = d.useState([])
      , {settings: n} = Cs();
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = localStorage.getItem("stride-planner-tasks");
        if (y) {
            const g = JSON.parse(y);
            t(g.map(b => ({
                ...b,
                dueDate: new Date(b.dueDate),
                createdAt: new Date(b.createdAt),
                updatedAt: new Date(b.updatedAt),
                lastNotifiedAt: b.lastNotifiedAt ? new Date(b.lastNotifiedAt) : void 0
            })))
        }
    }
    , []),
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = setInterval( () => {
            const g = new Date
              , b = new Date(g.getTime() + 6e4);
            n.notifications.enableReminders && e.forEach(m => {
                var v;
                if (m.completed || m.isArchived || !m.time)
                    return;
                const [x,w] = m.time.split(":").map(Number)
                  , h = new Date(m.dueDate);
                if (h.setHours(x, w, 0, 0),
                h >= g && h < b) {
                    if (m.lastNotifiedAt && new Date(m.lastNotifiedAt).getTime() === h.getTime())
                        return;
                    console.log(`[useTasks] Sending notification for task due now: ${m.title}`),
                    (v = window.electronAPI) == null || v.showNotification({
                        title: m.title,
                        body: m.description || "Напоминание о задаче"
                    }).then(S => {
                        S && n.notifications.notificationSound && new Audio("/notification.mp3").play().catch(k => console.error("Error playing sound:", k))
                    }
                    ),
                    i(m.id, {
                        lastNotifiedAt: h
                    })
                }
            }
            )
        }
        , 6e4);
        return () => {
            clearInterval(y)
        }
    }
    , [e, n.notifications]),
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = () => {
            if (!n.automation.autoArchiveCompleted)
                return;
            const b = e.filter(m => m.completed && !m.isArchived);
            if (b.length > 0) {
                console.log(`[Automation] Archiving ${b.length} completed tasks.`);
                const m = e.map(x => x.completed && !x.isArchived ? {
                    ...x,
                    isArchived: !0,
                    updatedAt: new Date
                } : x);
                r(m)
            }
        }

                return;

              , m = e.filter(x => new Date(x.dueDate) < b && !x.completed);

                console.log(`[Automation] Deleting ${m.length} overdue tasks.`);

                r(x)
            }
        }

        y(),
        g()
    }
    , [e, n.automation]);

        t(y),
        localStorage.setItem("stride-planner-tasks", JSON.stringify(y))

        };

    }

        } : m);

    }
    ;

        tasks: e,
        addTask: o,

            r(e.filter(g => g.id !== y))

        ,

            i(y, {
                isArchived: !0
            })

            i(y, {
                isArchived: !1
            })

            const g = new Date(y);
            return g.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0),
            e.filter(b => {
                if (b.isArchived)
                    return !1;
                const m = new Date(b.dueDate);
                if (m.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0),
                m > g)
                    return !1;
                if (!b.recurrenceRule || b.recurrenceRule === "none")
                    return m.getTime() === g.getTime();
                const x = g.getDay();
                switch (b.recurrenceRule) {
                case "daily":
                    return !0;
                case "weekly":
                    return m.getDay() === x;
                case "monthly":
                    return m.getDate() === g.getDate();
                case "yearly":
                    return m.getDate() === g.getDate() && m.getMonth() === g.getMonth();
                case "weekdays":
                    return x >= 1 && x <= 5;
                case "weekends":
                    return x === 0 || x === 6;
                default:
                    return !1
                }
            }
            )
        }
        ,
        exportTasks: () => {

              , g = new Blob([y],{

            m.click()

        ,

                        ...S,
                        dueDate: new Date(S.dueDate),
                        createdAt: new Date(S.createdAt),
                        updatedAt: new Date(S.updatedAt)

                    r(v),
                    g()
                } catch (h) {
                    b(h)
                }
            }
            ,
            m.readAsText(y)
        }
        )
    }
}

function LO({isOpen: e, onClose: t, date: n}) {
    const {getTasksForDate: r, addTask: o, updateTask: i, deleteTask: s, archiveTask: a} = li()
      , [l,u] = d.useState(!1)
      , [f,p] = d.useState(null);
    if (!n)
        return null;
    const y = r(n).sort( (w, h) => w.time && h.time ? w.time.localeCompare(h.time) : w.time ? -1 : h.time ? 1 : 0)
      , g = w => {
        f ? i(f.id, w) : o(w),
        u(!1),
        p(null)
    }
      , b = () => {
        p(null),
        u(!0)
    }
      , m = w => {
        p(w),
        u(!0)
    }
      , x = w => {
        switch (w) {
        case "high":
            return "border-l-priority-high";
        case "medium":
            return "border-l-priority-medium";
        case "low":

function Rn(e) {
    return e.split("-")[0]

    return e.split("-")[1]

function Xd(e) {
    return e === "x" ? "y" : "x"

function Jd(e) {
    return e === "y" ? "height" : "width"

function Dc(e) {
    return e.replace(/start|end/g, t => $E[t])

const eh = ["left", "right"]
  , th = ["right", "left"]
  , VE = ["top", "bottom"]
  , UE = ["bottom", "top"];
function HE(e, t, n) {
    switch (e) {
    case "top":

    case "right":

    default:

    }

function GE(e, t, n, r) {

function Wa(e) {

function Ba(e) {
    const {x: t, y: n, width: r, height: o} = e;

function nh(e, t, n) {
    let {reference: r, floating: o} = e;
    const i = nn(t)
      , s = Zd(t)
      , a = Jd(s)
      , l = Rn(t)
      , u = i === "y"
      , f = r.x + r.width / 2 - o.width / 2
      , p = r.y + r.height / 2 - o.height / 2
      , y = r[a] / 2 - o[a] / 2;
    let g;
    switch (l) {
    case "top":
        g = {
            x: f,
            y: r.y - o.height
        };
        break;
    case "bottom":
        g = {
            x: f,
            y: r.y + r.height
        };
        break;
    case "right":
        g = {
            x: r.x + r.width,
            y: p
        };
        break;
    case "left":
        g = {
            x: r.x - o.width,
            y: p
        };
        break;
    default:
        g = {
            x: r.x,
            y: r.y
        }
    }
    switch (oi(t)) {
    case "start":
        g[s] -= y * (n && u ? -1 : 1);
        break;
    case "end":
        g[s] += y * (n && u ? -1 : 1);
        break
    }
    return g
}

function dT(e, t) {
    const n = Math.abs(t.top - e.y)
      , r = Math.abs(t.bottom - e.y)
      , o = Math.abs(t.right - e.x)
      , i = Math.abs(t.left - e.x);
    switch (Math.min(n, r, o, i)) {
    case i:
        return "left";
    case o:
        return "right";
    case n:
        return "top";
    case r:
        return "bottom";
    default:
        throw new Error("unreachable")
    }
}
function fT(e, t, n=5) {
    const r = [];
    switch (t) {
    case "top":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y + n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break;
    case "bottom":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y - n
        });
        break;
    case "left":
        r.push({
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x + n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break;
    case "right":
        r.push({
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y - n
        }, {
            x: e.x - n,
            y: e.y + n
        });
        break
    }
    return r
}

function hT(e, t) {

}

function gT(e) {
    if (e.length <= 1)
        return e.slice();

    for (let r = 0; r < e.length; r++) {
        const o = e[r];
        for (; t.length >= 2; ) {
            const i = t[t.length - 1]
              , s = t[t.length - 2];
            if ((i.x - s.x) * (o.y - s.y) >= (i.y - s.y) * (o.x - s.x))
                t.pop();
            else
                break
        }
        t.push(o)
    }
    t.pop();
    const n = [];
    for (let r = e.length - 1; r >= 0; r--) {
        const o = e[r];
        for (; n.length >= 2; ) {
            const i = n[n.length - 1]
              , s = n[n.length - 2];

                n.pop();
            else
                break
        }
        n.push(o)
    }

    t.length === 1 && n.length === 1 && t[0].x === n[0].x && t[0].y === n[0].y ? t : t.concat(n)
}

var Rl = class {
    constructor() {
        this.listeners = new Set,
        this.subscribe = this.subscribe.bind(this)
    }
    subscribe(e) {
        return this.listeners.add(e),
        this.onSubscribe(),
        () => {
            this.listeners.delete(e),
            this.onUnsubscribe()
        }
    }
    hasListeners() {
        return this.listeners.size > 0
    }
    onSubscribe() {}
    onUnsubscribe() {}
}

function Sh(e, t) {
    const {type: n="all", exact: r, fetchStatus: o, predicate: i, queryKey: s, stale: a} = e;
    if (s) {
        if (r) {
            if (t.queryHash !== mf(s, t.options))
                return !1
        } else if (!as(t.queryKey, s))
            return !1
    }

        const l = t.isActive();
        if (n === "active" && !l || n === "inactive" && l)
            return !1
    }
    return !(typeof a == "boolean" && t.isStale() !== a || o && o !== t.state.fetchStatus || i && !i(t))
}
function Ch(e, t) {
    const {exact: n, status: r, predicate: o, mutationKey: i} = e;
    if (i) {
        if (!t.options.mutationKey)
            return !1;

                return !1
        } else if (!as(t.options.mutationKey, i))

    }

}
function mf(e, t) {

function ss(e) {

function as(e, t) {
    return e === t ? !0 : typeof e != typeof t ? !1 : e && t && typeof e == "object" && typeof t == "object" ? Object.keys(t).every(n => as(e[n], t[n])) : !1
}
function Iw(e, t) {
    if (e === t)
        return e;
    const n = Eh(e) && Eh(t);
    if (n || $c(e) && $c(t)) {

          , o = r.length

          , s = i.length

            u++) : (a[p] = Iw(e[p], t[p]),

        }

    }

}
function Eh(e) {
    return Array.isArray(e) && e.length === Object.keys(e).length
}
function $c(e) {
    if (!kh(e))
        return !1;
    const t = e.constructor;
    if (t === void 0)

}
function kh(e) {

zn = function(t) {
    const n = r => {
        switch (t.type) {
        case "failed":
            return {
                ...r,
                failureCount: t.failureCount,
                failureReason: t.error
            };
        case "pause":
            return {
                ...r,
                isPaused: !0
            };
        case "continue":
            return {
                ...r,
                isPaused: !1
            };
        case "pending":
            return {
                ...r,
                context: t.context,
                data: void 0,
                failureCount: 0,
                failureReason: null,
                error: null,
                isPaused: t.isPaused,
                status: "pending",
                variables: t.variables,
                submittedAt: Date.now()
            };
        case "success":
            return {
                ...r,
                data: t.data,
                failureCount: 0,
                failureReason: null,
                error: null,
                status: "success",
                isPaused: !1
            };
        case "error":
            return {
                ...r,
                data: void 0,
                error: t.error,
                failureCount: r.failureCount + 1,
                failureReason: t.error,
                isPaused: !1,
                status: "error"
            }
        }
    }
    ;
    this.state = n(this.state),
    Qe.batch( () => {
        j(this, qt).forEach(r => {
            r.onMutationUpdate(t)
        }
        ),
        j(this, Ye).notify({
            mutation: this,
            type: "updated",
            action: t
        })
    }
    )
}

function eo(e) {

function zh(e, t="") {

function bi(e, t) {

        return e.one;

}

  , Ef = ["воскресенье", "понедельник", "вторник", "среду", "четверг", "пятницу", "субботу"];
function Dj(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    switch (e) {
    case 0:
        return "'в прошлое " + t + " в' p";
    case 1:
    case 2:
    case 4:
        return "'в прошлый " + t + " в' p";
    case 3:
    case 5:
    case 6:
        return "'в прошлую " + t + " в' p"
    }
}
function Hh(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    return e === 2 ? "'во " + t + " в' p" : "'в " + t + " в' p"
}
function _j(e) {
    const t = Ef[e];
    switch (e) {
    case 0:
        return "'в следующее " + t + " в' p";
    case 1:
    case 2:
    case 4:
        return "'в следующий " + t + " в' p";
    case 3:
    case 5:
    case 6:
        return "'в следующую " + t + " в' p"
    }
}
const Aj = {
    lastWeek: (e, t, n) => {
        const r = e.getDay();
        return Uh(e, t, n) ? Hh(r) : Dj(r)
    }
    ,
    yesterday: "'вчера в' p",
    today: "'сегодня в' p",
    tomorrow: "'завтра в' p",
    nextWeek: (e, t, n) => {
        const r = e.getDay();
        return Uh(e, t, n) ? Hh(r) : _j(r)
    }
    ,
    other: "P"
}
  , Ij = (e, t, n, r) => {
    const o = Aj[e];
    return typeof o == "function" ? o(t, n, r) : o
}

  , iO = ["Пн", "Вт", "Ср", "Чт", "Пт", "Сб", "Вс"];
function sO({tasks: e, onTaskCreate: t, onTaskUpdate: n, onTaskArchive: r, getTasksForDate: o, openDaySidebar: i}) {
    const [s,a] = d.useState(new Date)
      , [l,u] = d.useState(null)
      , [f,p] = d.useState(!1)
      , [y,g] = d.useState(null)
      , [b,m] = d.useState("")
      , x = d.useMemo( () => e.filter(T => !T.isArchived && (T.title.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase()) || T.description && T.description.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase()) || T.tags && T.tags.some(F => F.toLowerCase().includes(b.toLowerCase())))), [e, b])
      , w = mr(s, {
        weekStartsOn: 1
    })
      , h = R2(s, {
        weekStartsOn: 1
    })
      , v = [];
    let S = w;
    for (; S <= h; )
        v.push(S),
        S = Ih(S, {
            days: 1
        });
    const C = T => {
        a(F => Ih(F, {
            weeks: T === "prev" ? -1 : 1
        }))
    }
      , k = T => {
        i(T)
    }
      , E = (T, F) => {
        F.stopPropagation(),
        g(T),
        u(null),
        p(!0)
    }
      , N = T => {
        y ? n(y.id, T) : l && t({
            ...T,
            dueDate: l
        }),
        p(!1)
    }
      , O = T => {
        switch (T) {
        case "high":
            return "bg-priority-high";
        case "medium":
            return "bg-priority-medium";
        case "low":
            return "bg-priority-low";
        default:
            return "bg-muted"
        }
    }
    ;
    return c.jsxs("div", {
        className: "h-full flex flex-col",
        children: [c.jsxs("div", {
            className: "flex items-center justify-between p-4 border-b",
            children: [c.jsxs("div", {
                className: "flex items-center gap-4",
                children: [c.jsx(Ue, {
                    variant: "outline",
                    size: "icon",
                    onClick: () => C("prev"),
                    children: c.jsx(ey, {
                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                    })
                }), c.jsxs("h2", {
                    className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                    children: [Vh(w, "d MMMM", {
                        locale: Gh
                    }), " - ", Vh(h, "d MMMM yyyy", {
                        locale: Gh
                    })]
                }), c.jsx(Ue, {
                    variant: "outline",
                    size: "icon",
                    onClick: () => C("next"),
                    children: c.jsx(ty, {
                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                    })
                })]
            }), c.jsx("div", {
                className: "w-1/3",
                children: c.jsx($t, {
                    placeholder: "Поиск...",
                    value: b,
                    onChange: T => m(T.target.value)
                })
            })]
        }), c.jsx("div", {
            className: "flex-1 p-4",
            children: c.jsxs("div", {
                className: "grid grid-cols-7 gap-1",
                children: [iO.map(T => c.jsx("div", {
                    className: "p-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground",
                    children: T
                }, T)), v.map( (T, F) => {
                    const I = new Date().toDateString() === T.toDateString()
                      , U = o(T).filter(M => x.includes(M));
                    return c.jsx(ot, {
                        className: L("min-h-[100px] p-2 cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50", I && "ring-2 ring-primary"),
                        onClick: () => k(T),
                        children: c.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "flex flex-col h-full",
                            children: [c.jsx("span", {
                                className: L("text-sm font-medium mb-1", I && "text-primary font-bold"),
                                children: T.getDate()
                            }), c.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex-1 space-y-1",
                                children: [U.slice(0, 3).map(M => c.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: L("p-1 rounded text-xs cursor-pointer hover:opacity-80 text-white", O(M.priority), M.completed && "opacity-50 line-through"),
                                    onClick: G => E(M, G),
                                    children: [M.title.substring(0, 20), M.title.length > 20 && "..."]
                                }, M.id)), U.length > 3 && c.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "text-xs text-muted-foreground",
                                    children: ["+", U.length - 3, " еще"]
                                })]
                            }), U.length === 0 && c.jsx("div", {
                                className: "flex-1 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity",
                                children: c.jsx(ml, {
                                    className: "h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground"
                                })
                            })]
                        })
                    }, F)
                }
                )]
            })
        }), c.jsx(Fl, {
            open: f,
            onOpenChange: p,
            task: y,
            selectedDate: l,
            onSubmit: N,
            onArchive: r
        })]
    })
}
const li = () => {
    const [e,t] = d.useState([])
      , {settings: n} = Cs();
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = localStorage.getItem("stride-planner-tasks");
        if (y) {
            const g = JSON.parse(y);
            t(g.map(b => ({
                ...b,
                dueDate: new Date(b.dueDate),
                createdAt: new Date(b.createdAt),
                updatedAt: new Date(b.updatedAt),
                lastNotifiedAt: b.lastNotifiedAt ? new Date(b.lastNotifiedAt) : void 0
            })))
        }
    }
    , []),
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = setInterval( () => {
            const g = new Date
              , b = new Date(g.getTime() + 6e4);
            n.notifications.enableReminders && e.forEach(m => {
                var v;
                if (m.completed || m.isArchived || !m.time)
                    return;
                const [x,w] = m.time.split(":").map(Number)
                  , h = new Date(m.dueDate);
                if (h.setHours(x, w, 0, 0),
                h >= g && h < b) {
                    if (m.lastNotifiedAt && new Date(m.lastNotifiedAt).getTime() === h.getTime())
                        return;
                    console.log(`[useTasks] Sending notification for task due now: ${m.title}`),
                    (v = window.electronAPI) == null || v.showNotification({
                        title: m.title,
                        body: m.description || "Напоминание о задаче"
                    }).then(S => {
                        S && n.notifications.notificationSound && new Audio("/notification.mp3").play().catch(k => console.error("Error playing sound:", k))
                    }
                    ),
                    i(m.id, {
                        lastNotifiedAt: h
                    })
                }
            }
            )
        }
        , 6e4);
        return () => {
            clearInterval(y)
        }
    }
    , [e, n.notifications]),
    d.useEffect( () => {
        const y = () => {
            if (!n.automation.autoArchiveCompleted)
                return;
            const b = e.filter(m => m.completed && !m.isArchived);
            if (b.length > 0) {
                console.log(`[Automation] Archiving ${b.length} completed tasks.`);
                const m = e.map(x => x.completed && !x.isArchived ? {
                    ...x,
                    isArchived: !0,
                    updatedAt: new Date
                } : x);
                r(m)
            }
        }

                return;

              , m = e.filter(x => new Date(x.dueDate) < b && !x.completed);

                console.log(`[Automation] Deleting ${m.length} overdue tasks.`);

                r(x)
            }
        }

        y(),
        g()
    }
    , [e, n.automation]);

        t(y),
        localStorage.setItem("stride-planner-tasks", JSON.stringify(y))

        };

    }

        } : m);

    }
    ;

        tasks: e,
        addTask: o,

            r(e.filter(g => g.id !== y))

        ,

            i(y, {
                isArchived: !0
            })

            i(y, {
                isArchived: !1
            })

            const g = new Date(y);
            return g.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0),
            e.filter(b => {
                if (b.isArchived)
                    return !1;
                const m = new Date(b.dueDate);
                if (m.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0),
                m > g)
                    return !1;
                if (!b.recurrenceRule || b.recurrenceRule === "none")
                    return m.getTime() === g.getTime();
                const x = g.getDay();
                switch (b.recurrenceRule) {
                case "daily":
                    return !0;
                case "weekly":
                    return m.getDay() === x;
                case "monthly":
                    return m.getDate() === g.getDate();
                case "yearly":
                    return m.getDate() === g.getDate() && m.getMonth() === g.getMonth();
                case "weekdays":
                    return x >= 1 && x <= 5;
                case "weekends":
                    return x === 0 || x === 6;
                default:
                    return !1
                }
            }
            )
        }
        ,
        exportTasks: () => {

              , g = new Blob([y],{

            m.click()

        ,

                        ...S,
                        dueDate: new Date(S.dueDate),
                        createdAt: new Date(S.createdAt),
                        updatedAt: new Date(S.updatedAt)

                    r(v),
                    g()
                } catch (h) {
                    b(h)
                }
            }
            ,
            m.readAsText(y)
        }
        )
    }
}

function LO({isOpen: e, onClose: t, date: n}) {
    const {getTasksForDate: r, addTask: o, updateTask: i, deleteTask: s, archiveTask: a} = li()
      , [l,u] = d.useState(!1)
      , [f,p] = d.useState(null);
    if (!n)
        return null;
    const y = r(n).sort( (w, h) => w.time && h.time ? w.time.localeCompare(h.time) : w.time ? -1 : h.time ? 1 : 0)
      , g = w => {
        f ? i(f.id, w) : o(w),
        u(!1),
        p(null)
    }
      , b = () => {
        p(null),
        u(!0)
    }
      , m = w => {
        p(w),
        u(!0)
    }
      , x = w => {
        switch (w) {
        case "high":
            return "border-l-priority-high";
        case "medium":
            return "border-l-priority-medium";
        case "low":
            return "border-l-priority-low";
        default:
            return "border-l-muted"
        }
    }
    ;
    return c.jsxs(c.Fragment, {
        children: [c.jsx(xw, {
            open: e,
            onOpenChange: t,
            children: c.jsxs(hf, {
                className: "w-[400px] sm:w-[540px]",
                children: [c.jsxs(Sw, {
                    children: [c.jsxs(Cw, {
                        children: ["Задачи на ", n.toLocaleDateString("ru-RU", {
                            day: "numeric",
                            month: "long",
                            year: "numeric"
                        })]
                    }), c.jsx(Ew, {
                        children: "Просмотр и управление задачами на выбранный день."
                    })]
                }), c.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "py-4",
                    children: [c.jsxs(Ue, {
                        onClick: b,
                        className: "w-full mb-4",
                        children: [c.jsx(ml, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4 mr-2"
                        }), "Добавить задачу"]
                    }), c.jsx("div", {
                        className: "space-y-3",
                        children: y.length > 0 ? y.map(w => c.jsxs("div", {
                            onClick: () => m(w),
                            className: L("p-3 border-l-4 rounded-r-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-muted", x(w.priority)),
                            children: [c.jsx("h4", {
                                className: `font-semibold ${w.completed ? "line-through text-muted-foreground" : ""}`,
                                children: w.title
                            }), w.time && c.jsx("p", {
                                className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                children: w.time
                            }), w.description && c.jsx("p", {
                                className: "text-sm mt-1 text-muted-foreground",
                                children: w.description
                            })]
                        }, w.id)) : c.jsx("p", {
                            className: "text-center text-muted-foreground py-8",
                            children: "На этот день задач нет."
                        })
                    })]
                })]
            })
        }), c.jsx(Fl, {
            open: l,
            onOpenChange: u,
            task: f,
            selectedDate: n,
            onSubmit: g,
            onDelete: s,
            onArchive: a
        })]
    })
}
mv(document.getElementById("root")).render(c.jsx(IO, {}));
